title: Create a Moe anthropomorphism of Yamp Mascot.
body:
For marketing purpose, I propose to create a Moe anthropomorphism
of the Yamp rabbit character. Research have show huge increase in exposure when a product are turn into cute anime girl. We can use the new character for NFT purpose.
author: 0x18A456132d95c027A55113222233b6128777EdB8
